original_title: Brooklyn: Coney Island Avenue - Ocean Parkway
text:
Brighton Beach.
Atlantic Ocean, Brighton Beach from Coney Island Ave., to Oriental point. At the right is the Manhattan Beach and Oriental Hotels.

About 1905.?

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

Brooklyn: Coney Island Avenue - Ocean Parkway

text:
Prospect Park Gate No. 5, at the intersection of Coney Island Avenue, Ocean Parkway, and Parkside Avenue.

About 1913

Urbrock Collection

title: Brooklyn: Prospect Park - Gate No. 5.

original_title: Brooklyn: Coney Island Avenue - Ocean Parkway
text:
(1) Coney Island Ave., north from Reigelman Boardwalk, showing a part of Coney Island Ave., shut off from vehicular traffic. Also seen is the Brighton Beach train coming out of Brighton Beach Ave, this is the B.M.T.

November 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, another view.

November 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
